<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-45-0530 </DOCNO><TEXT>Acceptance tests of the film processing system are a prerequisite of theacceptance tests of the X-ray equipment, and are the basis of the recurrentin-service tests. All data taken during the acceptance tests have tobe recorded, filed and given to the supervising expert, and kept fora period of ten years. DIN 6868, part 2 recommends daily testing of thefilm processing system. The legal provisions provide for weekly tests,but experience gathered during the last few months has shown that weeklytests are not enough and thus cannot be recommended.</TEXT></DOC>